<h3><span class="mw-headline" id="Lions_as_heraldic_charge">Lions as heraldic charge</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Lion_(heraldry)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6" title="Edit section: Lions as heraldic charge"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h3>
<h4><span class="mw-headline" id="Lions_rampant">Lions rampant</span><span class="mw-editsection"><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">[</span><a href="/w/index.php?title=Lion_(heraldry)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7" title="Edit section: Lions rampant"><span>edit</span></a><span class="mw-editsection-bracket">]</span></span></h4>
